{"tid":2249000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左得把口聲緩 香港仲可以做到啲咩","createTime":"2020-10-19T04:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T04:57:55.000Z","uid":296014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"46353868f078522e38049764158ad8218be39647","tid":2249000,"uid":296014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"上年香港抗爭時<br />\n有台灣捐物資到香港 去支持香港人<br />\n幫我地打強心針<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令我地知道香港人唔係孤身作戰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年泰國抗爭左已經好一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個禮拜出埋水炮車<br />\n理應泰國人都好需要物資<br />\n但我見佢地既裝備其實唔係好夠<br />\n想藉著捐物資 比佢地知道香港人除左得把口 都會行動<br />\n比佢地知道泰國人都唔孤單<br />\n<br />\n我想知有咩方法可以捐物資到泰國<br />\n或者可以係連登搵多啲人一齊捐過去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66931956099b3b74e8fe44979363439921cef0ea","tid":2249000,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"返工 返工 &amp; 返工"},{"pid":"0ce2a1976c1758f706c125ce47c5b0be7373afa9","tid":2249000,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:46:54.000Z","msg":"自己幾個fd捐，<br />\n跟住放上twitter啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係之後又有人問，<br />\nd支出咁貴/費用去哂邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beda5bd6064aa5afdc9ad233a759a22d2f457c13","tid":2249000,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}